# Strategy Lab runtime data — must NOT be tracked in git. These files are a
# live database that grows as trades happen; if git tracks them, every
# `git reset --hard` / redeploy checkout wipes them back to their last
# committed (empty) state, destroying trade history even though the real
# fills still exist at the broker.
data/strategy_trades.json
data/activity.json
